```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([VM vMotion Initiated]) --> PreCheck{Pre-Migration<br/>Checks}
    
    PreCheck -->|Fail| Error1[Display Error<br/>Migration Cancelled]
    PreCheck -->|Pass| Reserve[Reserve Resources<br/>on Target Host]
    
    Reserve --> Shadow[Create Shadow VM<br/>on Target]
    Shadow --> Memory1[Copy Memory Pages<br/>Iteratively]
    
    Memory1 --> QuiesceCheck{Is Memory<br/>Copy Rate<br/>Acceptable?}
    
    QuiesceCheck -->|No, Continue| Memory1
    QuiesceCheck -->|Yes| Quiesce[Quiesce VM<br/>Brief Pause]
    
    Quiesce --> CopyFinal[Copy Final<br/>Memory State]
    CopyFinal --> Switch[Switch Execution<br/>to Target Host]
    
    Switch --> Resume[Resume VM<br/>on Target]
    Resume --> Cleanup[Cleanup Source<br/>Remove Shadow VM]
    
    Cleanup --> Complete([vMotion Complete])
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style Complete fill:#90EE90
    style Error1 fill:#FFB6C6
    style Quiesce fill:#FFE6AA
    style Switch fill:#FFE6AA
    
    classDef checkStyle fill:#E6F3FF,stroke:#4A90E2
